title: Edward Teller
tags: 2003 coop Demo Evoke Lyrics video Vocals Windows
info:
Lyrics (with repetitions omitted):

I am not Edward Teller
My conscience does not grow on trees
And even though it clearly doesn't count
I want you all to understand my argument

I am not Edward Teller
I see red, yellow, blue and white
And even though it clearly doesn't matter
I show my plans for anyone to hear

You are not Edward Teller
You do not have to prove it to yourself
And even though you cannot change your talent
You will achieve what others seldom reach

They are not Edward Teller
And neither cause nor reason they will see
And even though they will say it's annoying
It's just a lousy piece of poetry
